<h2 class="bold font-l">The Grey Lanterns</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Spoony, Linkara and Dr. Insano manage to successfully save the multiverse by convincing the audience that Warrior #4 is irrelevant and have now become Grey Lanterns, the Guardians of Not-Giving-A-Crap. It makes more sense in context. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="njayc9" data-video-descrip="Coupled with Ape Political's attacks, Political Nihilist's nihilism beams were able to suck Ancom of all of his passion and turning him into Post-Left." data-video-title="Political Nihilist" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/njayc9_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/njayc9.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/ThePowerOfApathy" data-video-tropename="The Power of Apathy" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WebVideo/Jreg" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/njayc9.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Political Nihilist</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="h8bdxh" data-video-descrip="He seems to share this power with Political Nihilist, Nihilist's nihilism beams and Ape Political's physical assaults robbing Ancom of his passion and turning him into Post-Left." data-video-title="Ape Political" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/h8bdxh_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/h8bdxh.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/ThePowerOfApathy" data-video-tropename="The Power of Apathy" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WebVideo/Jreg" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/h8bdxh.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Ape Political</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="8x1t4q" data-video-descrip="Much like Political Nihilist and Apepolitical, Anti-Radical has the power to make ideologies more centrist. In his case, his knife is lined with venom that makes any ideology less extreme, nearly turning both Ancap and Libertarian into Neo-Liberals before Ancap kills him." data-video-title="Anti-Radical" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/8x1t4q_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/8x1t4q.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/ThePowerOfApathy" data-video-tropename="The Power of Apathy" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WebVideo/Jreg" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/8x1t4q.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Anti-Radical</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
